lyse ihrer Produktionsprozesse und aufgrund einer kritischen Erörterung der Architektur aus handlungs- und machttheoretischer Perspektive.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aAvantgarde. 4aKontext. 4aMacht. 4aNetztheorie. 4aRaum. 4aWissen. 4aÄsthetik. 7aARCHITECTURE / Urban & Land Use Planning.2bisacsh  aAesthetics.  aSpace.1 aReuter, Wolf, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2010-2013z9783110352856oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Kunst Arch. 2010-2013z9783110370720oZDB-23-TKA0 cprintz978383761553140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839415535?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839415535423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839415535/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TKAc2010d2013  aZDB-23-TSOc2010d2013